<TEXT>
<P>
LAGOS, April 16 (Xinhua) -- Nigeria exported 93 million U.S.
Dollars of non-oil products in 1996, the Nigerian Association of
Chambers of Commerce, Industry, Mines and Agriculture (NACCIMA)
said in its latest edition of NACCIMA News.
</P>
