<HEADLINE> Macao to Host China Books, Audio-Video Works Fair </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
MACAO, April 17 (Xinhua) -- Macao will host a major exhibition
of Chinese books and audio-video works between April 18 and 21 as
part of a cultural exchange program.
</P>
<P>
Co-sponsored by the Macao Foundation and the China National
Publications Import and Export Corporation (CNPIEC), the book fair
will present more than 5,000 copies of books, tapes and compact
disks.
