(OCBC) Foreign was the biggest loser as it declined by 30 cents to
end at 17.5 Singapore dollars. The Development Bank of Singapore
(DBS) Foreign, Malaya Cement, and the United Overseas Bank (UOB)
Foreign fell by 20 cents each to close at 17.8, 2.6, and 15
