55 vehicles which was inadequate to clear the nearly 800 tons of
garbage collected daily in the city.
</P>
<P>
Consequently about 150 tons of garbage remained uncleared daily
in the city, the sources said.
</P>
<P>
A workforce of 22,000 persons are to be deployed in the city to
collect, transport and dispose garbage at the clearing points.
