3.828 billion US dollars, a drop of 2.8 percent over last year's
same period.
</P>
<P>
The favorable trade balance in the first quarter was 1.22
billion US dollars, a rise of 690 million dollars over last year.
</P>
<P>
Electro-mechanical equipment has continued to dominate the
city's exports, the sources said. 
