back from one set down to eliminate Chinese Taipei's number one
Wang Shi-ting, 4-6, 6-3, 6-3.
</P>
<P>
Australia's Annabel Ellwood kept her lucky run with a 6-1, 6-4
win over Janet Lee of the United States. 
