<HEADLINE> Bangladesh's Main Opposition May Agitate for CEC's </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
DHAKA, April 17 (Xinhua) -- The main opposition Bangladesh
Nationalist Party (BNP) may launch fresh anti-government agitation
after the holly Eid Day of April 18, which is likely to
concentrate on its demand for the resignation of Chief Election
Commissioner (CEC) Abu Hena.
