in communications and natural gas shipments. They will set up
joint ventures in transport, and raise the annual trade turnover
between the three nations to 20-50 million U.S. dollars.
</P>
<P>
Heads of state of the three countries would exchange visits
soon to promote cooperation, the foreign ministers told reporters
after their talks. 
